  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Technician (M&E)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Description:</strong></p><p>-Rostered shifts</p><p>-West area<br /></p><p><strong>Job Duties:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Carry out routine preventive maintenance and minor repairs for building M&E systems, including HVAC, electrical, plumbing, fire protection and basic carpentry</p></li><li><p>Troubleshoot and rectify faults in electrical circuits, panels, motors, pumps and other building equipment</p></li><li><p>Support inspections, testing and servicing of lifts, generators and UPS systems</p></li><li><p>Monitor Building Management System (BMS) and respond promptly to alarms, system irregularities and power or equipment failures</p></li><li><p>Operate building systems safely and ensure accurate recording of operational readings and conditions</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with safety regulations, statutory requirements and internal SOPs</p></li><li><p>Maintain maintenance logs, checklists and technical documentation, and support audits and inspections</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with external vendors and contractors for specialized maintenance and repair works</p></li><li><p>Support facilities operations during shutdowns, renovations and new system installations</p></li><li><p>Liaise with tenants or occupants to minimize disruption during maintenance activities</p></li><li><p>Provide emergency response support for M&E breakdowns and participate in standby or 24/7 duty roster when required<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>- Min Nitec in Mechanical / Electrical / Building Services Engineering or related field.<br />- At least 2 years of relevant experience in building maintenance, facilities management, or a similar role.<br /></p><p>Interested Applicants, please click Apply Now<br /><br />Chow Zi Qing<br />R2199258<br />Revup Proservices Pte Ltd<br />EA.24C2366</p>",
